{"tha-ap409:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap409:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap409:0.3":"Hemakattheraapadana ","tha-ap409:1.1":"“Pabbharakutam nissaya, ","tha-ap409:1.2":"anomo nama tapaso; ","tha-ap409:1.3":"Assamam sukatam katva, ","tha-ap409:1.4":"pannasale vasi tada. ","tha-ap409:2.1":"Siddham tassa tapo kammam, ","tha-ap409:2.2":"siddhipatto sake bale; ","tha-ap409:2.3":"Sakasamannavikkanto, ","tha-ap409:2.4":"atapi nipako muni. ","tha-ap409:3.1":"Visarado sasamaye, ","tha-ap409:3.2":"paravade ca kovido; ","tha-ap409:3.3":"Pattho bhumantalikkhamhi, ","tha-ap409:3.4":"uppatamhi ca kovido. ","tha-ap409:4.1":"Vitasoko nirarambho, ","tha-ap409:4.2":"appaharo alolupo; ","tha-ap409:4.3":"Labhalabhena santuttho, ","tha-ap409:4.4":"jhayi jhanarato muni. ","tha-ap409:5.1":"Piyadassi nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap409:5.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap409:5.3":"Satte taretukamo so, ","tha-ap409:5.4":"karunaya phari tada. ","tha-ap409:6.1":"Bodhaneyyam janam disva, ","tha-ap409:6.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap409:6.3":"Cakkavalasahassampi, ","tha-ap409:6.4":"gantva ovadate muni. ","tha-ap409:7.1":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap409:7.2":"mamassamamupagami; ","tha-ap409:7.3":"Na dittho me jino pubbe, ","tha-ap409:7.4":"na sutopi ca kassaci. ","tha-ap409:8.1":"Uppata supina mayham, ","tha-ap409:8.2":"lakkhana suppakasita; ","tha-ap409:8.3":"Pattho bhumantalikkhamhi, ","tha-ap409:8.4":"nakkhattapadakovido. ","tha-ap409:9.1":"Soham buddhassa sutvana, ","tha-ap409:9.2":"tattha cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap409:9.3":"Titthanto va nisinno va, ","tha-ap409:9.4":"sarami niccakalikam. ","tha-ap409:10.1":"Mayi evam sarantamhi, ","tha-ap409:10.2":"bhagavapi anussari; ","tha-ap409:10.3":"Buddham anussarantassa, ","tha-ap409:10.4":"piti me hoti tavade. ","tha-ap409:11.1":"Kalanca punaragamma, ","tha-ap409:11.2":"upesi mam mahamuni; ","tha-ap409:11.3":"Sampattepi na janami, ","tha-ap409:11.4":"ayam buddho mahamuni. ","tha-ap409:12.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap409:12.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap409:12.3":"Sanjanapesi attanam, ","tha-ap409:12.4":"‘aham buddho sadevake’. ","tha-ap409:13.1":"Sanjanitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap409:13.2":"piyadassim mahamunim; ","tha-ap409:13.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap409:13.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap409:14.1":"‘Anne pithe ca pallanke, ","tha-ap409:14.2":"asandisu nisidare; ","tha-ap409:14.3":"Tuvampi sabbadassavi, ","tha-ap409:14.4":"nisida ratanasane’. ","tha-ap409:15.1":"Sabbaratanamayam pitham, ","tha-ap409:15.2":"nimminitvana tavade; ","tha-ap409:15.3":"Piyadassissa munino, ","tha-ap409:15.4":"adasim iddhinimmitam. ","tha-ap409:16.1":"Ratane ca nisinnassa, ","tha-ap409:16.2":"pithake iddhinimmite; ","tha-ap409:16.3":"Kumbhamattam jambuphalam, ","tha-ap409:16.4":"adasim tavade aham. ","tha-ap409:17.1":"Mama hasam janetvana, ","tha-ap409:17.2":"paribhunji mahamuni; ","tha-ap409:17.3":"Tada cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap409:17.4":"sattharam abhivadayim. ","tha-ap409:18.1":"Piyadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap409:18.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap409:18.3":"Ratanasanamasino, ","tha-ap409:18.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap409:19.1":"‘Yo me ratanamayam pitham, ","tha-ap409:19.2":"amatanca phalam ada; ","tha-ap409:19.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap409:19.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap409:20.1":"Sattasattati kappani, ","tha-ap409:20.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap409:20.3":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap409:20.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap409:21.1":"Dvattimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap409:21.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap409:21.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap409:21.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap409:22.1":"Sonnamayam rupimayam, ","tha-ap409:22.2":"pallankam sukatam bahum; ","tha-ap409:22.3":"Lohitangamayanceva, ","tha-ap409:22.4":"lacchati ratanamayam. ","tha-ap409:23.1":"Cankamantampi manujam, ","tha-ap409:23.2":"punnakammasamanginam; ","tha-ap409:23.3":"Pallankani anekani, ","tha-ap409:23.4":"parivaressare tada. ","tha-ap409:24.1":"Kutagara ca pasada, ","tha-ap409:24.2":"sayananca maharaham; ","tha-ap409:24.3":"Imassa cittamannaya, ","tha-ap409:24.4":"nibbattissanti tavade. ","tha-ap409:25.1":"Satthi nagasahassani, ","tha-ap409:25.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap409:25.3":"Suvannakaccha matanga, ","tha-ap409:25.4":"hemakappanavasasa. ","tha-ap409:26.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","tha-ap409:26.2":"tomarankusapanibhi; ","tha-ap409:26.3":"Imam paricarissanti, ","tha-ap409:26.4":"ratnapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap409:27.1":"Satthi assasahassani, ","tha-ap409:27.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap409:27.3":"Ajaniyava jatiya, ","tha-ap409:27.4":"sindhava sighavahino. ","tha-ap409:28.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","tha-ap409:28.2":"illiyacapadharibhi; ","tha-ap409:28.3":"Tepimam paricarissanti, ","tha-ap409:28.4":"ratnapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap409:29.1":"Satthi rathasahassani, ","tha-ap409:29.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap409:29.3":"Dipa athopi veyaggha, ","tha-ap409:29.4":"sannaddha ussitaddhaja. ","tha-ap409:30.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","tha-ap409:30.2":"capahatthehi vammibhi; ","tha-ap409:30.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap409:30.4":"ratnapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap409:31.1":"Satthi dhenusahassani, ","tha-ap409:31.2":"dohanna pungavusabhe; ","tha-ap409:31.3":"Vacchake janayissanti, ","tha-ap409:31.4":"ratnapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap409:32.1":"Solasitthisahassani, ","tha-ap409:32.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap409:32.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap409:32.4":"amukkamanikundala. ","tha-ap409:33.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap409:33.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap409:33.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap409:33.4":"ratnapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap409:34.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap409:34.2":"gotamo nama cakkhuma; ","tha-ap409:34.3":"Tamandhakaram vidhamitva, ","tha-ap409:34.4":"buddho loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap409:35.1":"Tassa dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap409:35.2":"pabbajissatikincano; ","tha-ap409:35.3":"Tosayitvana sattharam, ","tha-ap409:35.4":"sasanebhiramissati. ","tha-ap409:36.1":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap409:36.2":"kilese ghatayissati; ","tha-ap409:36.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap409:36.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap409:37.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","tha-ap409:37.2":"yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","tha-ap409:37.3":"Uttamattham patthayanto, ","tha-ap409:37.4":"sasane viharamaham. ","tha-ap409:38.1":"Idam pacchimakam mayham, ","tha-ap409:38.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap409:38.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap409:38.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap409:39.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap409:39.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap409:39.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap409:40.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap409:40.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap409:40.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap409:41.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap409:41.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap409:41.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap409:42.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma hemako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap409:43.1":"Hemakattherassapadanam sattamam. ","tha-ap409:43.2":"Sattarasamam bhanavaram. "}